    <item>
      <title>Glint 0.1.0</title>
      <sparkle:version>202606091325</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 13:27:25 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[<div style="font-family:-apple-system,sans-serif;"><h3>更新内容 · What's new in 0.1.0</h3><ul>
    <li><strong>pane: scrollback + render alignment + hook isolation</strong><br><span style="color:#666">终端面板:补滚动支持 / 修渲染断层 / dev 与 prod 独立 hook</span></li>
    <li>chrome: rework keyboard shortcuts and sidebar search</li>
    <li><strong>i18n: wire sidebar / palette / about through LocalizedStringKey</strong><br><span style="color:#666">让侧栏、命令面板、关于页面真正走中文(顺手把侧栏搜索接上、通道根据构建判断)</span></li>
    <li><strong>readme: prefix upgrade with brew update</strong><br><span style="color:#666">升级命令前面加上 brew update,否则 tap 元数据不刷新拉不到新版</span></li>
    <li>release: appcast for v0.0.4</li>
  </ul></div>]]></description>
      <enclosure url="https://github.com/chenbstack/glint/releases/download/v0.1.0/Glint-0.1.0.dmg" length="10092499" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="OzT16e54/TZavUvjlPtdXAnvEdzcvobWwt2Rz+Y4VXOd1djvDIfGa8mg8m1zn3dIGsm+Z9BQUczELY56uCmPDA==" />
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Glint 0.0.4</title>
      <sparkle:version>202606091213</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.0.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 12:14:24 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description>&lt;div style="font-family:-apple-system,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;h3&gt;更新内容 · What's new in 0.0.4&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;release: properly ad-hoc codesign the bundle after archive&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color:#666"&gt;用 codesign 重签 .app,避免 Sparkle 拒绝安装&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;appcast: drop sparkle:releaseNotesLink, render local CDATA instead&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color:#666"&gt;appcast 去掉外链,直接渲染本地 CDATA 里的更新说明&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;appcast: use build number for sparkle:version + bilingual notes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color:#666"&gt;appcast 改用构建号作为 sparkle:version 字段,加入双语更新说明&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;release: appcast for v0.0.3&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
      <enclosure url="https://github.com/chenbstack/glint/releases/download/v0.0.4/Glint-0.0.4.dmg" length="10077091" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="GeZNdt8lmtkXYGMzig/Ea7E3y7c+7gbNPbv0ysHbfT4iC5LVODis37VvUlVdRKU7p2fo1iexhzgH9hTfcqriBQ==" />
